    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一人称生存恐怖游戏，伴随着幽灵、恶魔与通灵板。故事发生在一个虚构的、灵异的美国森林，Green Creek。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >记录死亡，拼尽全力生存下去</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在森林的夜晚，为了记录幽灵和你存在的证据战斗下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用通灵板与亡者对话。运用你的相机和音响设备记录他们，但这也会让你处于极度危险之中。除了躲避起来，没有其他用来防御幽灵和恶魔的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745950/extras/7c03fa4844fa441aa896568b41ce5a69.poster.avif?t=1728311631\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745950/extras/7c03fa4844fa441aa896568b41ce5a69.webm?t=1728311631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745950/extras/7c03fa4844fa441aa896568b41ce5a69.mp4?t=1728311631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的设备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你记录越多的幽灵，你就会得到越多的点数。使用点数可以升级你的设备和解锁新的区域。但是你要保证你能活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
